33:37.000 --> 33:39.100
a mr. shawn thompson?

33:39.100 --> 33:42.100
i believe that you're a regular
player in his horror films.

33:42.200 --> 33:43.100
gabriel:
as you may know,

33:43.100 --> 33:47.300
mr. thompson tragically died
