34:20.600 --> 34:22.500
which is why we wanted
to talk to you.

34:23.500 --> 34:25.100
to me? why?

34:25.100 --> 34:27.400
well, you were having an affair
with christine, weren't you?

34:28.100 --> 34:29.400
are you kidding?

34:30.699 --> 34:31.500
<i>having a -- no.</i>

34:31.500 --> 34:32.900
<i>who told you that?
i never --</i>

34:32.900 --> 34:34.600
<i>uh, hold on.
hold on --</i>

