34:47.900 --> 34:48.900
we, uh --

34:49.600 --> 34:51.600
i met christine
on one of shawn's films.

34:51.600 --> 34:53.699
she visited the set
during one of the stunts,

34:53.699 --> 34:56.600
but, i swear,
it was just a friendship.

34:57.600 --> 34:59.500
ask him if he rides a motorcycle.
what are you doing?!

34:59.500 --> 35:00.700
i'm seeing a motorcycle.

35:00.700 --> 35:02.000
give that to me!
but -- no! but --

35:02.000 --> 35:04.400
let go!
i'm seeing an angry wind!

35:04.400 --> 35:06.600
brenda, this is important!
ask about the angry wind!

35:06.600 --> 35:09.200
<i>provenza: i am tired of
